    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, meticulously preserved to maintain its peak mechanical integrity. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission offers precise shift throws, coupled with a factory-spec M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. Critically, this chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service, ensuring the structural and internal longevity of the platform. The suspension geometry remains true, with no bushing compliance issues or damping degradation. A turn-key specimen for the collector demanding an uncompromised driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
