    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been pampered since day one, stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint look wet to the touch; you won't find a single stone chip or swirl mark here. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state, with the premium leather upholstery still retaining its factory-fresh scent and supple texture. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all records meticulously documented. With ultra-low mileage and a history of adult-only ownership, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Serious inquiries only for this investment-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48900.0,
